name: Leonard's Ego
overview:
Leonard’s Ego build WordPress plugins and themes used by thousands of websites.

The company specialises in developing extensions for the rapidly growing WooCommerce ecosystem. Their flagship product is the popular Subscriptions extension for WooCommerce, sold in partnership with WooThemes. They are also responsible for the PayPal Digital Goods payment gateway extension.

In addition to their commercial products, the company have released a range of free WordPress plugins to the WordPress open-source community, including the mildly popular Multisite User Management and Social Connect plugins. Both of which have been downloaded tens of thousands of times from the WordPress.org free plugin repository.
